<div id="baby-shower-section" class="baby-shower-section activity-section p-3 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-uppercase mb-3" data-aos="fade-up">baby showers</h2>
    <h5 data-aos="fade-up">We host babyshowers at Hart on Sundays and we are open from 10Am till 3pm</h5>
    <p class="alternate-day" data-aos="fade-up">(If you are looking for alternate day, drop us a message to see what we can do)</p>
    <p data-aos="fade-up">We can host groups of 2 people up to 120 people and can offer a table, area, private room, half venue and full venue hire depending on the size of your party.</p>
    <p data-aos="fade-up">We do not charge for venue hire but there is a minimum spend and deposit required. The cost of which is dependent on the date you book for. Please get in touch to find out more.</p>
    <p data-aos="fade-up">You can order just drinks or opt in for our breakfast/main/set menu or a buffet!.</p>
    <p data-aos="fade-up">We do not offer any set packages but can create one to suit your budget, theme, requirements and needs. Just ask!</p>
    <p data-aos="fade-up">Go as wild as you like with decorations and games. The only thing we say no to absolutely <strong>no confetti...please!</strong>.</p>
    <p data-aos="fade-up">Drop us a message on Instagram, Facebook or Email now to find out more.</p>
</div>
